  "text": "Male C57BL/6 mice from Jackson Laboratories and the Id4-eGFP (LT-11B6) transgenic reporter line [CITATION_1] were maintained with ad libitum normal laboratory diet. All experiments using animals were approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee of the University of Texas at San Antonio (Assurance A3592-01) and were performed in accordance with the National Institutes of Health Guide for the Care and Use of Laboratory Animals.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "9345114"
